@startuml
title LowCortisol Platform - Report Backend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Report Backend Bounded Context" {
  class "Application" as Backend_report_Application <<layer>>
  class "Domain" as Backend_report_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Backend_report_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Interfaces REST" as Backend_report_Interfaces_REST <<layer>>
}

Backend_report_Interfaces_REST ..> Backend_report_Application : commands / queries
Backend_report_Application ..> Backend_report_Domain : model and policies
Backend_report_Application ..> Backend_report_Infrastructure : repository ports / adapters
Backend_report_Infrastructure ..> Backend_report_Domain : persistence mapping
Backend_report_Interfaces_REST ..> Backend_report_Domain : resources from aggregates

note bottom of Backend_report_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/backend/layers/report.
end note

@enduml
